export enum ContractStatus {
  INITIALISED = 'initialised',
  TESTED = 'tested',
  ERROR = 'error',
  SIGNED = 'signed',
  SENT = 'sent',
  REJECTED = 'rejected',
  DEPLOYED = 'deployed',
  CALLED = 'called',
}
